pageContext.claim: “We are all here today for the same reason -- because we believe in that beautiful, beautiful phrase that hasn’t been used so much over the last three decades: Made in the USA.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump now calls for Americans to “buy American, hire American.” But this is misleading. Trump has a long history of outsourcing a variety of his own products. The Fact Checker has counted a total of 12 countries where Trump products were manufactured (China, the Netherlands, Mexico, India, Turkey, Slovenia, Honduras, Germany, Bangladesh, Indonesia, Vietnam and South Korea).
